   context — never inherited as a stale draft from today's position.
   The §6 stage list is direction, not specification.
3. **Substrate discipline, unchanged.** Every substrate edit enters
   plan-mode and runs `/v4-axiom-check` first (CLAUDE.md §6); the
   SUBSTRATE_CONSTRUCTION §3 transplant + §4 dissection gates apply;
